text: Motion

Tet-ten, teteten,
te-te-teten...!

──The part where you go "teteten".
This part.

Pyeh...! Was, was I off...?
Um──

It's okay.
C'mon. One, and.

Hinana wants to do it with Toru-senpai too～!

Te-Ten, teteten,
Te-Te-Teten...

Toru-chan...
You sure are incredible, aren't you...?

...
You were doing just fine too, Koito.

E-Eheheh...
Of course, though! I can handle this much...!

so we have to take it seriously...!
...You're right.

Motion
Why that job?

──Erm... the live show, I take it? I thought it was a
pretty good proposal. You've got reservations, then?

Indeed I do.
The values I hold are distinct from yours, after all.

...Everyone is getting their singing and dancing done,
and I thought it was about time we had a concrete goal.

The fact you're going to make so many viewers aware of you,
I think, is going to be hugely important experience.

──You're very kind, running your mouth, aren't you.
The ones bearing the full brunt of this? The merchandise?
If anything is to happen, I will not forgive you for it.
